    "On the other hand, sales and marketing managers may employ ML and deep learning to develop targeted promotional strategies.",
    "Organizational considerations, such as management's familiarity with AI in digital marketing, affect how quickly businesses can adopt AI technology (Nair & Gupta, 2021).",
    "Most research articles agreed that AI might significantly impact content development for online advertising.",
    "Its impact can be felt throughout a wide range of industries now.",
    "In addition, several experts have pointed to the opportunities big data and AI present for learning more about consumers' decision-making processes."
